glass window where, authorities said Friday, a thief drove off the night before 
in either a Mercedes-Benz or customized Nissan worth about $40,000. The car 
reportedly was last spotted heading for the Harbor Freeway. The vehicle's make 
is unknown because of an ongoing inventory. MIKE SERGIEFF / For The Times 
