<TEXT>
<P>
In an attempt to stop a 272-unit housing development on 220 acres in the San 
Gabriel Mountain foothills, the Friends of La Vina, an Altadena group opposed 
to the project, filed a lawsuit Friday against Los Angeles County. 
</P>
<P>
