<HEADLINE>
<P>
GIRLS' BASKETBALL ROUNDUP 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
In other league games: 
</P>
<P>
Kennedy 66, Bolsa Grande 41 -- Valerie Ruiz scored 26 points and had six 
assists to lead Kennedy (10-9, 6-3) at home. 
</P>
<P>
