SYNDICATION; TELEVISION INDUSTRY; TELEVISION NETWORKS; MOTION PICTURE 
ASSOCIATION OF AMERICA; MURDOCH, RUPERT; NEWS CORP LTD; FOX INC; GOVERNMENT 
REGULATION 
</P>
