<P>
MURDERS -- MEXICO; ARRESTS -- MEXICO; FALKENSTEIN, CLAUDE; ENGELS, PATRICIA; 
CONFESSIONS; ROBBERIES -- MEXICO 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
